705
00:45:44.325 --> 00:45:47.871
<i>What is hip hop?
Is this the voice
from the street?</i>

706
00:45:47.954 --> 00:45:51.040
<i>Is this why you guys
are just so angry?</i>

707
00:45:51.124 --> 00:45:52.333
<i>No, dawg.</i>

708
00:45:52.417 --> 00:45:54.043
<i>It's chill,
it's chill, it's chill.</i>

709
00:45:56.838 --> 00:46:00.550
<i>Right, okay. Listen,
can you rap about anything?</i>

710
00:46:00.633 --> 00:46:03.136
<i>For example, could you rap
