00:46:57.190 --> 00:46:59.192
Paid gig?

734
00:46:59.275 --> 00:47:00.443
No.

735
00:47:00.610 --> 00:47:01.778
Better get back
to it then.

736
00:47:01.861 --> 00:47:04.197
Thirty-four identical essays
