a little bit of the old...

738
00:47:10.912 --> 00:47:13.289
You know,
afternoon delight?

739
00:47:31.266 --> 00:47:32.392
Wow!

740
00:47:33.101 --> 00:47:34.644
You look incredible.

741
00:47:34.727 --> 00:47:36.396
Oh... Ooh!

742
00:47:36.479 --> 00:47:38.356
Let's see the dress.

743
00:47:39.983 --> 00:47:41.109
Is it vintage?

744
00:47:41.192 --> 00:47:42.235
No, it's brand new.

