782
00:49:18.581 --> 00:49:20.291
She's doing incredibly well.

783
00:49:20.416 --> 00:49:22.168
Yeah, yeah.

784
00:49:22.251 --> 00:49:24.087
Well, we both are.

785
00:49:24.921 --> 00:49:28.216
I've got some really, really
exciting stuff coming up.

786
