800
00:50:21.561 --> 00:50:23.998
I just thought you were going
to be writing this novel,
that's all.

801
00:50:24.022 --> 00:50:26.149
And I will.
But I have to earn a living.

802
00:50:26.232 --> 00:50:28.711
More to the point, I enjoy it.
