new console games
coming at you.

851
00:53:27.914 --> 00:53:31.167
Until then, night owls,
keep gaming.

852
00:53:35.922 --> 00:53:39.008
Do I really have to
say "smoking hot"?

853
00:53:40.718 --> 00:53:43.554
It's just I'm 32,
for God's sake.

854
00:53:45.431 --> 00:53:47.183
