905
00:56:17.833 --> 00:56:19.502
There's my boy!

906
00:56:19.585 --> 00:56:20.937
Better luck
next time, son.
Thank you.

907
00:56:20.961 --> 00:56:23.506
Well, I'm still
very proud of you.

908
00:56:25.174 --> 00:56:26.675
Oh, isn't this fun?

909
00:56:26.759 --> 00:56:28.928
