for not changing the locks.

928
00:57:29.321 --> 00:57:30.489
Looking good, Ian.

929
00:57:30.614 --> 00:57:31.824
You can get stuffed, Emma.

930
00:57:31.907 --> 00:57:32.907
Is that from your act?

931
00:57:32.950 --> 00:57:35.995
No, though I have
got this new thing
I've been working on.

