1501
01:40:37.532 --> 01:40:38.616
I know.

1502
01:40:41.327 --> 01:40:42.829
But we will see
each other again.

1503
01:40:42.996 --> 01:40:44.497
I know we will.

1504
01:40:47.000 --> 01:40:48.293
Goodbye, Dex.

